{"tid":2381077,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.14新城市衝突技術員襲警罪脫 官指督察證供不可靠","createTime":"2021-01-26T10:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T12:33:26.000Z","uid":56115,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d36a169a94d136c7be499b9557a38356c68e808f","tid":2381077,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"前年7月14日有團體發起沙田區大遊行，反對修訂逃犯條例及要求落實五大訴求。其間新城市廣場爆發警民衝突，有電腦技術員被指襲警，否認控罪受審。案中聲稱遇襲的督察昨指現場片段拍攝不到事發一刻，但揚言襲擊正好發生於被告離開鏡頭及重新出現之間的一秒內。裁判官今早裁決，直言片段顯示被告在指稱施襲時間與督察相距十多米；<span class=\"red\">若如督察所述，被告要在一秒間由原先垂下手持的傘、變為舉高雨傘向下施襲、繼而逃去，實在艱難，裁定督察證供不可靠，被告罪名不成立。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，香官直言被告自己的行為無疑也是可疑的，在警方施放胡椒噴劑前，被告已在場揮舞雨傘。"},{"pid":"60f4ac09bb374252059a2db1a461a3a4c7634edb","tid":2381077,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210126/QLQHZZN75ZC25MSUQTK6ZLBAEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210126%2FQLQHZZN75ZC25MSUQTK6ZLBAEI%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv8SEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=8854a63b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210126%2FQLQHZZN75ZC25MSUQTK6ZLBAEI%2F&h=4e483659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210126/QLQHZZN75ZC25MSUQTK6ZLBAEI/</a>"},{"pid":"3d11075b7efbc01523ee8ea724d84555ea4406e5","tid":2381077,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQAaupv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQAaupv.png&h=da5163d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"909b1b43f93c4d40b5e9e2b2076a102c07984926","tid":2381077,"uid":227588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"天下武功，唯快不破！<br />\n如果成個閃電俠咁，仲俾你捉L到咩？"},{"pid":"78b5210a184283d9eca6ccf07abee1ef252d3ece","tid":2381077,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,